name: POP UP IS TO STAND OUT

metadata.name: ELEKTRA
metadata.description: After the people of planet Earth colonized the planet Mars, the Martians faced A threat that aliens known as Borax, a colonizer, would attack them and damage the planet Mars. Elektra, the president of the Martian Republic's daughter and famed for her young beauty, has been motivated to become a space ranger. Elektra was not your typical princess; she was confident in her abilities and willing to fight for her people rather than sit on the throne. She eventually becomes an expert in hand-to-hand combat and can fight even without the space gun as her skills develop.
